2. In this Act-                                                 Interpre-
                                                                  tation.
    “Bank” means the Inter-American Development Bank;
    “company” means a company incorporated in Jamaica
         and carrying on business therein;
    “Minister” means the Minister responsible for finance;
    “statutory authority” means any body established
         directly by statute and exercising powers vested in
         such body by law for a public purpose.
